org.cicirello.core - A Java library of utilities and data structures

Copyright © 2019-2023 Vincent A. Cicirello.

About org.cicirello.core

This library provides some of the core utilities and data structures used in several of our other libraries and projects.

The source code repository is hosted on GitHub. The source code is licensed under the GNU General Public License Version 3 (GPLv3). For more information see the org.cicirello.core website.
